    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# XLM-RoBERTa Fine-tuning — `career_position` Annotation (Broad Sectors)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Fine-tune `xlm-roberta-base` to classify job descriptions into CoREx **broad sector** codes (first digit only).\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Task:** annotation / `career_position`  \\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Input:** `job_description_label` (silver standard text)  \\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Output:** broad sector code (e.g. `1` = Executive triangle, `4` = Politics)  \\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Requirements:** `pip install corex_eval[bert]`\"\n",
    "   ],\n",
    "   \"id\": \"909ad2f32e5642eb\"\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
